headline: 23rd Annual MIT Sloan CFO Summit Concludes with Change-Led, Forward-Focused Insights
summary: CAMBRIDGE, Mass., November 21, 2025--The MIT Sloan CFO Summit, the premier conference for Chief Financial Officers, which brings together more than 400 CFOs, senior financial executives and MIT faculty, successfully concluded its 23rd annual event. Themed "Change Management: How CFOs Lead, Structure and Manage Change," the conference offered a full day of formal presentations, panel discussions and high-level networking.

headline: FedEx Corp. Board Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: MEMPHIS, Tenn., November 21, 2025--The Board of Directors of FedEx Corp. (NYSE: FDX) today declared a quarterly cash dividend of $1.45 per share on FedEx Corp. common stock, in line with the company’s continued focus on delivering stockholder value. The dividend is payable January 6, 2026, to stockholders of record at the close of business on December 15, 2025.

headline: Air cargo impact from post-crash MD-11 grounding seen as 'minimal,' analysts say
summary: Air cargo could be impacted by the UPS and FedEx fleet groundings ahead of the busy holiday season.
